    "Newer plagiarism detection technologies can also be used to counter potential academic dishonesty.",
    "In order to facilitate the incorporation and evidence-based use of AI systems in medical education, more investigation and assessment are required.",
    "When used in conjunction with conventional teaching techniques, Chat GPT has the potential to significantly enhance student learning and provide a more dynamic and engaging learning environment [17].",
